    <stitle>13 SPEED AND 18 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON RTLO-713/18 SERIES - REMOVE - CLUTCH HOUSING</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="remove" graphiccount="2">
        <title>CLUTCH HOUSING</title>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>The clutch release mechanism must be removed.</para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the nuts and washers from inside the clutch housing (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1300729">Figure 29</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1300729" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1300729" filename="../figg13/g1300729.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
                <caption>Figure 29. Remove Nuts and Washers From Clutch Housing</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the bolts from inside the clutch housing (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1300729">Figure 29</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Jar clutch housing to break the gasket seal (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1300730">Figure 30</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1300730" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1300730" filename="../figg13/g1300730.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
                <caption>Figure 30. Pull Clutch Housing From Transmission Case</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Pull the clutch housing from the studs and transmission case (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1300730">Figure 30</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the gasket and clean all mounting surfaces of gasket material (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1300730">Figure 30</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
